name: ABC CAMO REVERSIBLE DOWN VEST MENS
description:
Product: 0ZXDNM144010L
Manufacturer: CHINA
Material: 100% POLYESTER

A BATHING APE®︎ has a long history with down jackets. The 2023 A/W line is made with recycled down from Kawada Feathers, an expert in the industry. This sustainable choice has garnered attention for its eco-friendly properties. Not only is down plush and soft, but it can also stay resilient for over a century.

The popular ABC CAMO print adds a unique element to the jacket, while the reversible side sports the iconic ONE POINT APE head design for a more laid-back style.

name: SEAGULL EMBROIDERY GODHEAD PRINT RELAX FIT DENIM JACKET
description:
2ESHTM4DJ8001RXDN




Taking inspiration from the KOINOBORI culture, this jacket features a Godhead riding a Koinobori on the back, along with a mixed technique logo of embroidery and printing. The front showcases a dual-color embroidered Seagull design with extended lines. The overall jacket has distressed and washed effects, and it is also equipped with military-inspired accessories like logo hanging ribbons and triangular inner plackets on the front closure, showcasing EVISU's exquisite craftsmanship and quality. It creates a rich and vivid aesthetic that is both interesting and captivating.

Relax Fit
91% Cotton, 9% Viscose
12.6 oz denim
Dual-color embroidered seagull with extended lines
'Godhead riding a Koinobori' print and logos with mixed techniques
Frayed edges and distressed effects
Logo hanging ribbons and front closure with triangular line design
Button fastening, 4 pockets




FIT & STYLING: RELAX

name: EAGLE AND SAMURAI EMBROIDERY RETRO DENIM JACKET
description:
2ESHTM3DJ118RXCX




Dreaming of a fierce eagle that lands on pine branches was considered a realisation of good fortune and luck back in Edo period. This denim jacket draws reference from retro design, featuring a back embroidery of eagle landing on pine tree with a courageous Samurai. The jacket is cut for a relax fit, and equipped with four pockets for optimal functionality.

Relax fit
Eagle, Samurai, EVISU logo and slogans, seagull embroidery
Long sleeves, 4 pockets
Button fastening
Godhead leather patch




FIT & STYLING: RELAX
